name it_salary_easy
title.ru Вакансии в ИТ (зарплаты) — очищенная версия
title.en IT Job Salaries — clean version
task regression
family ITSalary
variant easy
rows 750
columns 8
version 1.0
features experience_years, grade, specialization, city, work_format, company_segment, education
target salary_rub

description.ru Синтетический учебный датасет для предсказания зарплаты ИТ-специалиста по параметрам вакансии. Очищенная версия без пропусков и сложных типов данных.
description.en Synthetic educational dataset for predicting IT specialist salary based on job vacancy parameters. Clean version without missing values or complex data types.
source Synthetic dataset based on hh.ru and Habr Career salary statistics (2025-2026)
url https://github.com/tisomeke/ml_datasets_pascalabc.net
license MIT
synthetic true
missing no

feature.experience_years int
feature.grade categorical
feature.specialization categorical
feature.city categorical
feature.work_format categorical
feature.company_segment categorical
feature.education categorical
feature.salary_rub float

